Built for Mac OSX. 

Contents:
    
    scheduled_restart.sh
    --------------------
    Shell script to restart the compute. Makes sure no users are logged in 
    before performing a restart.
    
    scheduled_restart.plist
    -----------------------
    Property list file containing restart schedule. Change the integer
    values within the StartCalendarInterval block to set the time to restart.
    Remove the Weekday key to increase frequency to more than once a week.

    add.sh
    ---------
    Shell script to make install easier. Replace "USERNAME" in the src1 and 
    src2 variables with your username. Copy the scheduled_restart script and 
    plist to your desktop and run to install.

    remove.sh
    ----------
    Shell script to remove the scheduled restart. 
                
                